        public MDSChannel(java.lang.String sacresponse)
        Create a MDSChannel from a single epoch section of a SAC response from the MDS - This represents one epoch. Note if you expect multiple epochs then use the static function loadMDSResponse instead.
        Parameters:
        sacresponse - One epoch section in SAC "cooked response" format
